title: Under the Prairie Sky
description: In this Dateline classic, a mother of three mysteriously disappears. The only clue is her abandoned vehicle on a lonely Montana highway. Josh Mankiewicz reports. Originally aired on NBC on May 21, 2017.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
